---
import HeadersLayout from "./headers_layout.astro";
import Button from "./button.astro";
---

<div class="sektion-intro">
  <div class="fade"></div>
  <!-- Header -->
  <HeadersLayout overskrift="Vil du være frivillig?" desc="" color="#ffffff" />

  <!-- Content Container -->
  <div class="content-container">
    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="text-container">
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Arcu massa lorem quis egestas in eu lobortis cursus mi.. Commodo sagittis fringilla et etiam. Velit cursus sollicitudin sodales urna sapien non accumsan amet.. Purus ultrices libero tellus natoque.
        Mauris adipiscing sed lorem elementum. At mi porta lectus sit consectetur.. Varius ipsum suspendisse mauris eu posuere felis at congue dolor..
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/cooking-drawing.png" alt="cooking" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Button -->
  <div class="button-container">
    <Button text="Bliv frivillig" stroke="white" fill="none" />
  </div>
  <div class="fade_ned"></div>
</div>

<style>
  /* Mobile-First Styles */
  .sektion-intro {
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .content-container {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px; /* Reduced space between text and image */
  }

  .text-container {
    width: 100%;
  }

  p {
    color: white;
    font-family: var(--primary-font);
    font-size: var(--text-size);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .image-container {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .button-container {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 20px; /* Space between content and button */
  }

  /* Desktop Styles (Screen Width > 768px) */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    section {
      padding: 0; /* Remove padding to eliminate space on the sides */
    }

    .content-container {
      flex-direction: row; /* Text on the left, image on the right */
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      max-width: 1200px; /* Limit width for larger screens */
      margin: 0 auto; /* Center the container */
      gap: 20px; /* Reduced space between text and image */
    }

    .text-container {
      flex: 1; /* Text takes up 1 part of the space */
      margin-right: 30px; /* Small space between text and image */
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .image-container {
      flex: 1; /* Image takes up 1 part of the space */
      justify-content: flex-end; /* Align image to the right */
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding-right: 20%;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 90%; /* Make the image larger */
      height: auto;
      transform: scale(1.5);
    }

    .button-container {
      margin-top: 20px; /* Space between content and button */
      padding-left: 25%;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .button-container {
      justify-content: flex-start; /* Move button to the left */
      margin-top: 20px; /* Space between content and button */
      padding-right: 25%;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1260px) {
    .button-container {
      justify-content: flex-start; /* Move button to the left */
      margin-top: 20px; /* Space between content and button */
      padding-right: 10%;
    }
  }
  .fade {
    background: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 0%, rgba(0, 106, 250, 1) 100%);
    width: 2400px;
    margin-left: -100px;
    height: 30px;
    margin-top: -50px;
  }

  .fade_ned {
    background: rgb(0, 106, 250);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 106, 250, 1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 100%);
    width: 2400px;
    margin-left: -100px;
    margin-bottom: -85px;
    height: 50px;
  }
</style>
